# 🤖 Robot Arm Simulation & Control Guide

This folder contains the Gazebo simulation environment and the configuration needed to bridge the physics engine with ROS 2.

## 🛠️ Step 1: Install Dependencies
If this is the first time running the project, your professor needs to make sure all libraries are installed. Run this in the root of the workspace:

```bash
sudo apt update
rosdep install -i --from-path src --rosdistro jazzy -y
sudo apt install ros-jazzy-ros-gz ros-jazzy-joint-state-publisher-gui
